subtitle: This Month’s Benefits
content:
In addition to the recurring monthly GTA$500,000 deposited directly into your Maze Bank account, GTA+ Members who've signed up for this month (October 8 - November 5) will also receive:

— The Declasse Weaponized Tampa (Muscle)
— 50% off Biker Business Upgrades and Modifications
— 4X Rewards on the Featured Series
— The LS Death Metal Hoodie and Shorts
— And more

Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel anytime. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
